- Get and install the libsqlora8 library from http://www.poitschke.de/libsqlora8/
- cp your libsqlora8-config.h and sqlora.h to this directory or setup the 'include'-statements 
  regarding libsqlora8
- compile via make
- copy pam_oci8.so to /lib/security and make the proper changes to /etc/pam.d/ and /etc/pam.conf
- export all required Oracle enviroment varibles

